  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A pilot intervention of an existing intervention adapted for the returning warfighter
      population: a couples treatment for PTSD, Structured Approach Therapy (SAT), which emphasizes
      reducing the PTSD avoidance/numbing symptoms that are corrosive in families.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
